Content:
Coming up May 5th. Weather looks okay, but not great. If you live anywhere near Pine Bluff, Wisconsin, it's a must.

The Official Slimey Crud Café Racer Run® website
The Official Slimey Crud Café Racer Run® website, a bi-annual motorcycle ride starting in Pine Bluff, WI, find your own route to Leland, WI and then back to Pine Bluff. Come and go as you please, stay as long or as short as you wish. It's a rolling bike show and a event that is not to be missed.
